operator.name: Streaming Nest
operator.synopsis: Embedding operator to design and deploy streaming analytic processes.

operator.name: Aggregate Stream
operator.synopsis: This operator performs an aggregation on streamed data events in a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Duplicate Stream
operator.synopsis: This operator duplicates an input data stream in a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Filter Stream
operator.synopsis: This operator performs a filter operation on streamed data events in a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Neuro FlinkCEP
operator.synopsis: This operator performs an aggregation on streamed data events in a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Join Streams
operator.synopsis: This operator performs a join operation on two data streams in a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Connect Streams
operator.synopsis: This operator performs a join operation on two data streams in a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Kafka Sink
operator.synopsis: This operator provides a Kafka topic as a sink for a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Kafka Source
operator.synopsis: This operator provides a Kafka topic as a source to a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Map Stream
operator.synopsis: This operator performs a map operation on streamed data events in a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Union Stream
operator.synopsis: This operator takes the union of the input data streams in a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Select Stream
operator.synopsis: This operator performs a selection operation on the keys of streamed data events in a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Parse Field Stream
operator.synopsis: This operator parses the string value of the specified fields to JSON objects in streamed data events in a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Stringify Field Stream
operator.synopsis: This operator performs a stringify operation on the value of the specified fields of streamed data events in a streaming analytic workflow.

operator.name: Timestamp Stream
operator.synopsis: This operator puts a timestamp on the events of a stream (assigns it to the key provided as parameter).
